phatase<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Periportal Space of Mall<\/em><ul><li>Space Between the Portal Canal Stroma &amp; Outermost Hepatocytes<\/li><li>One of the Sites That Generates Lymph<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Specific Cells<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Hepatocytes<\/em><ul><li>The Primary Functional Cell<\/li><li>Conjugate Bilirubin<ul><li><a href=\"http:\/\/operativereview.com\/biliary-tract-anatomy-physiology\">*See Biliary Tract: Anatomy &amp; Physiology<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Remove Metabolic Wastes<\/li><li>Store Glycogen<\/li><li>Main Energy Source: Ketones<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Kupffer Cells<\/em><ul><li><strong>Macrophages<\/strong> within the Sinusoids<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li><em>Ito\/Stellate Cells<\/em><ul><li>Normally Quiescent (Store Vitamin A)<\/li><li><strong>Mediates Fibrosis<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-35c8a34\" data-id=\"35c8a34\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-92485e8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"92485e8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-10346 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Hepatic-Lobule.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Hepatic-Lobule.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/Hepatic-Lobule-300x135.jpg 30